import React from "react";
import Input from "../UI/Input/Input";

function CurrentBody() {
  let sexes = [Male, Female, Other];
  return (
    <form>
      <Input inputtype="input" type="text" name="age" placeholder="Your Age" />
      <Input inputtype="input" type="radio" name="sex" placeholder="Your Sex" />
      <Input
        inputtype="input"
        type="text"
        name="weight"
        placeholder="Your Weight"
      />
      <Input
        inputtype="input"
        type="text"
        name="height"
        placeholder="Your Height"
      />
      <Input
        inputtype="input"
        type="text"
        name="contagiousdiseases"
        placeholder="Do you have any contagious diseases"
      />
      <button>Validate Informations</button>
    </form>
  );
}

export default CurrentBody;
